      {
        "id": 4,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 5,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Fourth 1,500 Words",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Act 4: Fourth 1,500 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The final section of the story, where things reach their lowest point for the Hero before being wrapped up in a neat package. The Hero uses their skills and knowledge to escape a dire situation and defeat the Villain, demonstrating their character transformation. Any remaining mysteries looming over the story are cleared up over the course of the final conflict as the Hero takes hold of the situation – ending with a final twist in the plot, and a snappy punch line."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create even more difficulties for the Hero."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Hero be practically buried in their troubles (e.g. the Villain has them prisoner, the girl is assumed dead, all seems lost, and the Hero is about to die from a unique murder method)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Add one final surprise twist to the story near the end of this section (e.g. the Villain has a surprise identity or the treasure is worthless)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Wrap up and explain all storylines."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Add a final snappy punchline to conclude the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Does the suspense and menace continue to the last line?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 4 makes up the last 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Fourth 1,500 Words brings the story to its conclusion."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
