              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Act 3: Third 1,500 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "After the situation initially worsens, a glimmer of hope appears – the Hero seems to be getting closer to the solution to the looming menace / mystery. But this turns out to be a false hope, and the tension and stakes rise while the reader is swept along with swift, vivid action."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Add more grief and stress onto the Hero."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Let the Hero make some headway, perhaps cornering the Villain."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Add another physical conflict different from before."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Include a surprise twist which makes things much worse for the Hero, to end this section."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Does this section maintain suspense, deepen the menace, and place the Hero in a tough spot – while happening logically?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 3 makes up the third 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
