      {
        "id": 1,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 2,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "First 1,500 Words",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Act 1: First 1,500 Words",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The story begins with the Hero in a heap of trouble, and proceeds to get worse from there. Regardless of genre, a pulp story must have physical conflict and plot twists, suspense, and a genuine sense of menace."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the Hero as early as possible and stick them in a very difficult situation – hint at the mystery, menace, or problem they will have to solve around the first line."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show the Hero jumping into action to attempt to grasp the mystery, defeat the menace, or solve the problem."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce all of the characters and bring them in on the action."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Hero enter into a physical conflict near the end of this section."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Add a surprise twist in the plot at the end."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Does the story have suspense, create menace to the Hero, and proceed logically?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "A genuine pulp story should also contain at least one (or more) of the following elements:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "A unique murder method for the Villain to use"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "A unique thing for the Villain to be seeking"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "A unique location"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "A unique menace to hang over the Hero"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "First 1,500 Words brings the story to the 25% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
